DOC.brief_summary: This study evaluate whether laser acupuncture time embryo transfer ( follow vitro fertilization ) improve implantation rate . Patients randomize one 4 group time embryo transfer : 1 ) laser acupuncture , 2 ) needle acupuncture , 3 ) sham laser acupuncture , 4 ) treatment .
DOC.brief_title: Laser Acupuncture Before After Embryo Transfer Improves IVF Outcomes
DOC.criteria: All patient seek pregnancy via vitro fertilization study period Bleeding disorder ( due possible use needle ) Prior exposure acupuncture Preimplantation genetic screening diagnosis
